instructions: Instructions                                                                                                                                                                                                                 Preheat the oven to 300. Cut both types of peppers lengthwise and remove the seeds and veins. Lightly coat a heavy skillet with olive oil. Saut the peppers until they give off their juices and wilt. Season to taste with salt and pepper. Place the trout on a baking sheet and heat in the oven for 10 minutes.
